{"tid":2411220,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周浩鼎：不少「黑衫」人士旁聽「黑暴」案件，要求司法機構採取措施阻止有關情況發生","createTime":"2021-02-17T07:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T10:40:54.000Z","uid":50386,"like":42,"dislike":315,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"09c38f700337bf24cf3dd1b569bd59e2327ebe8b","tid":2411220,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:36:02.000Z","msg":"立法會人事編制小組通過開設1個高等法院上訴法庭法官職位。<span class=\"red\">民建聯周浩鼎質疑，不少「黑衫」人士旁聽「黑暴」案件，「都唔知係咪無形想向法官施壓」，要求司法機構交代會否採取果斷措施，阻止有關情況發生。</span>司法機構政務長梁悅賢指，如果出現秩序及保安問題，司法機構的人員和保安會適時阻止和驅散不合理行為，形容過去做法「一定程度上係有效」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/6CR3JI4ENZGA3GBG4OBO7OTFKY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2F6CR3JI4ENZGA3GBG4OBO7OTFKY%2F&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN20oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=6a98e4d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2F6CR3JI4ENZGA3GBG4OBO7OTFKY%2F&h=37a88298\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/6CR3JI4ENZGA3GBG4OBO7OTFKY/</a><br />\n<br />\n邊個著黑衫去旁聽<br />\n都要除咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68cd65779fd31f09b9729ce6de47933e5539ae77","tid":2411220,"uid":121197,"like":293,"dislike":0,"score":293,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:36:29.000Z","msg":"法官本身都著黑袍"},{"pid":"ca87d1f320adcabfd6b98d078540949135e4673d","tid":2411220,"uid":25794,"like":134,"dislike":0,"score":134,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:37:27.000Z","msg":"立法禁止黑衫囉, 同時立法表明白衫可以周街打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8aa084abe200534431bdacf7c83cbc260ab1a41","tid":2411220,"uid":23635,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:37:42.000Z","msg":"佢真係蠢唔係扮㗎喎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d56716cd02ba49a20600336363f28de40f8ed1","tid":2411220,"uid":216163,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:38:00.000Z","msg":"法官除左件衫先好做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97a974ceedb79d701cb891049f8b85ea052836c","tid":2411220,"uid":32816,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:42:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201031/bkn-20201031101728635-1031_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201031%2Fbkn-20201031101728635-1031_00822_001.html&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN20oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=f817531d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201031/bkn-20201031101728635-1031_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<em>沈官在判詞中指出，法庭認為不應把穿着黑衣的人隨意視為參與暴動或非法集結，這做法有危險性，有機會冤枉無辜的人，因在當下的情況，<span class=\"red\">除穿黑衣外，穿白色或其他顏色的人都可參與暴動</span></em><br />\n人地岩岩先判完<br />\n唔通黑衫就有壓力, <br />\n著晒白衫係咪就冇壓力? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb17d5a3249a2f853b605e01a927c58063b10fd4","tid":2411220,"uid":36901,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:42:48.000Z","msg":"賓周仔啟動左鬥紅mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71205c8b4cf47218c55ad95a86f0051639497470","tid":2411220,"uid":211466,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:42:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4EPd8QC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4EPd8QC.jpg&h=220fb08e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9fc7f34cf3a05112a1ff5d08e3129cbea7b0480","tid":2411220,"uid":89608,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:43:14.000Z","msg":"講野真係無腦, <br />\n香港未來就係呢班人話事, <br />\n都唔知點算"},{"pid":"d339fb7b31a3c28370fe75fd13721132816df487","tid":2411220,"uid":14103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:43:18.000Z","msg":"著咩色衫都冇自由了"},{"pid":"f4dd3a15614c35e92ae15a1578bee3b6abfeded9","tid":2411220,"uid":32588,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"